    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously got to see this beauty. It's in absolutely stunning condition\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've babied this car since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
