    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting a concours-level 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54B32 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six. This example is mechanically superlative, having undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance including a Dr. VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement with VAC coated shells, and a structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission offers precise gate engagement, paired with a factory variable M differential lock for optimal corner-exit traction. The chassis remains taut, utilizing refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers to maintain factory-spec kinematics. With zero oxidative wear and original paint depth readings, this vehicle represents a turn-key opportunity for the collector seeking peak analog performance.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
